post.body: I am a slave 老百姓 in a free country. I have two options: one is become unfree by getting unhired and have no money, and the other is become unfree by getting hired and get money but its use is interfered by agents.
So many agents but they never taught me that they are agents.
The work of agents is to increase their own value by interfering others development.
上海 may be a keyplace of recent years. 習近平 is from there and someone died there. But there are so many people there and slave can not find a clue.
Clue of my enemy, who fooled me, scared me, interfered me and honeytrapped me. There are some information about his daughters aber nicht ihre Sohn.
Naturally, the man talked about steel in that place is a agent.

They are composed of triangle, circle and cross.
We can not understand them because they communicate with pictures, not letters.
They are matrilineal because they speak but never write.

They say male take action on woman.
When we hear their voice, we die out.

Only english and 中文 survive here.
Why White and 黄色 do not try to understand each other.

Why Black and 黒 both have bad image.

What reside at the top of Ponte tower.

Why things flow, continue merging and separation.
Why two which can not match hath to meet.

Why is the link between them can not be seen.
Why is the origin never be unveild.
